"{\"uid\": \"abc.net.au-news-2024-03-16-shane-rose-paris-olympic-games-horror-equestrian-fall-103596670\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Personalise the news and  stay in the know  Emergency  Backstory  Newsletters  \\u4e2d\\u6587\\u65b0\\u95fb  BERITA BAHASA INDONESIA  TOK PISIN  Find any issues using dark mode?Please let us know  Sport  Topic:Equestrian  Shane Rose has won two silvers and a bronze in team eventing at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 275, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 92, \"end\": 108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"BAHASA INDONESIA\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indonesian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 198, \"end\": 208, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shane Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images:\\u00a0Kerry Marshall)  Triple Olympic medallist Shane Rose is in danger of missing the Paris Olympic Games after a heavy fall from his horse put him in intensive care.\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 290, \"end\": 304, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerry_Marshall\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kerry Marshall\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerry_Marshall\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kerry_Marshall\"}, {\"begin\": 332, \"end\": 342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shane Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shane_Rose\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 50-year-old team eventer was rushed to hospital after a tumble from his horse Virgil during a cross-country session on Thursday.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 585, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 535, \"end\": 541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\", \"score\": 0.7656625839801015, \"rank\": 0.2917609065547756, \"text\": \"Virgil\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He all but secured qualification for the Olympics by winning an event in New Zealand last weekend, with his team breaking the news of his accident on social media.\", \"from\": 587, \"to\": 750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9974823624301193, \"rank\": 0.0018930008295174141, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As the saying goes, peacock one day, feather duster the next!\\\"\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"a Facebook post read.\", \"from\": 816, \"to\": 837, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After a fantastic week in New Zealand, [where] Shane and Virgil secured their Olympic qualifications, this week Shane was bought back down to earth literally.\", \"from\": 839, \"to\": 998, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 866, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.9974823624301193, \"rank\": 0.0018930008295174141, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_rugby_league_team\"}, {\"begin\": 897, \"end\": 903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\", \"score\": 0.7656625839801015, \"rank\": 0.2917609065547756, \"text\": \"Virgil\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Virgil\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"During a cross country schooling session yesterday Shane suffered a nasty fall.\", \"from\": 1000, \"to\": 1080, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thankfully, his horse was not injured in the fall.\", \"from\": 1081, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The post said Rose had surgery to stabilise the fractures.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1147, \"end\": 1151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"score\": 0.9996895923850609, \"rank\": 0.0002876514182566585, \"text\": \"Rose\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rose_Tyler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"ABC Sport Daily is your daily sports conversation.\", \"from\": 1193, \"to\": 1243, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1193, \"end\": 1202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Grandstand\", \"score\": 0.9999999947890501, \"rank\": 5.2110238173259775e-09, \"text\": \"ABC Sport\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Grandstand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/ABC_Radio_Grandstand\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We dive into the biggest story of the day and get you up to speed with everything else that's making headlines.\", \"from\": 1244, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Shane is in good hands with a great medical team and support network,\\\" his team said.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1443, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While the timing is unfortunate, we are hopeful there is adequate time for him to recover and still be able to continue his preparation schedule for the Paris Olympics Games.\\\"\", \"from\": 1445, \"to\": 1621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Rose made headlines last month by wearing a \\\"mankini\\\" costume at a show-jumping event, with a complaint threatening his participation in Paris beforehe was cleared by Equestrian Australia following an investigation.\", \"from\": 1623, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1760, \"end\": 1765, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999963315531, \"rank\": 3.668671089314865e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1790, \"end\": 1810, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Equestrian Australia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Equestrian_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Based in Werombi, west of Sydney, Rose won team silver medals at the 2008 Beijing and 2021 Tokyo Olympics as well as a bronze in Rio in 2016.\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1981, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1849, \"end\": 1856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Werombi,_New_South_Wales\", \"score\": 0.669467902590356, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Werombi\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Werombi,_New_South_Wales\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Werombi,_New_South_Wales\"}, {\"begin\": 1866, \"end\": 1872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999999999827196, \"rank\": 1.068319277714082e-11, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 1874, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org